title: War in Octarius
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The first world of the Octarius Sector to feel Leviathan’s hunger was Orrok. Above the Orks’ settlements, thunder rumbled and the skies turned from blue to black as bio-ships entered orbit. Weirdboy psykers began to gibber in fear – something was clawing at the backs of their brains, something with an infinite hunger focused upon the Orks like the eye of a starving predator. Then the storm broke. 

